   177вҶ’## Options
   179вҶ’Options are defined with the `.option()` method, also serving as documentation for the options. Each option can have a short flag (single character) and a long name, separated by a comma, a space, or a vertical bar (`|`). To allow a wider range of short-ish flags than just single characters, you may also have two long options.
   180вҶ’
   181вҶ’```js
   182вҶ’program
