docs/release-policy.md
     1вҶ’# Release Policy
     3вҶ’We follow [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html), and limit breaking changes to major versions.
     4вҶ’
     5вҶ’There are major releases about every six months. We do a major release and bump the minimum required node version when LTS Node.js versions reach end-of-life.
     6вҶ’
